The OST's are amazing at adding emotion to certain events/scenes T_T There are not many contols which is convenient for the style where as the story for this game is exquisite, as it is highly captivating... trust me... I played hours and hours of this just to complete 100% of it.

Throughout the playthrough you learn more about the characters, allowing you to see the differences and how the characters react to certain events which opens up a connection between you and a certain character and THAT adds to the emotion on which certain ending you get. :3

Buuut, overall this game is impeccable and I highly recommend it for anyone who desires a free ARPG. :D it brought tears to my eyes ;_;

